{"tid":922170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撿到背包歸還物主卻拿走1800元 女子強辯「沒偷又沒搶」","createTime":"2018-11-30T07:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T07:15:02.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3226718a30c3d31b231803ba0e38d000d439f88e","tid":922170,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181130/_2018113012360277586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181130%2F_2018113012360277586.jpg&h=05e559bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日南京一名趙姓女子在火車上的廁所裏，撿到一個背包，趙女主動歸還給物主張女士，可是背包內卻少了一千八百元現金，警員從趙女手袋中內翻出這筆現金。趙女承認錢是自己拿的，但絲毫不認為自己做錯，還強辯稱「我就是沒想還給她，我又沒偷又沒搶。」<br />\n<br />\n據警方表示，張女士上廁所的時候，將自己的背包丟在廁所裏面了，但是自己回去的找的時候，卻已經不見了。當時張女也聯繫相關部門的人員詢問此事，看有甚麼好心人撿到自己的背包。<br />\n<br />\n想不到沒多久就有好心人過來將背包送還，當時看到自己背包失而復得，還非常高興。女失主現場即時檢查自己背包，看看有沒有甚麼東西不見了。背包裏是沒有物品掉失，但是背包內的1800元現金卻不翼而飛。當時，失主就問撿到自己背包的女子有沒有翻過自己背包，當時女子一口否定，自己沒有動過失主的背包。<br />\n<br />\n失主只好要求查看閉路電視錄像看看是誰將自己背包帶離廁所。通過閉路電視畫面發現一件十分奇怪的事情，送還背包以及撿到背包的人都是同一個人。當時警員就問女子，到底有沒有拿失主的錢。當時女子還一口否認。當時看到閉路電視片段，看來自己的罪行已經敗露，就只有承認。但是女子卻表示自己是撿的，並不是偷的，撿的到錢就是不願意給。最後，只有交給警方處理，將女子帶到派出所。趙女最緋承認自己拿了錢，還辯稱「我就是沒想還給她，我又沒偷又沒搶，不覺得自己有錯。」最終，趙女將錢歸還張女，並接受警方訓誡教育。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181130/_2018113012360351364.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181130%2F_2018113012360351364.jpg&h=5b04784d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/876934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F876934&d=XJlrGENh4tChnQbLgu56%2FQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=3cf583fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F876934&h=4dbfcec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/876934</a>"},{"pid":"ea953d13e218520f2a947a967406c8d3f59af7af","tid":922170,"uid":101783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"道亦有盜"},{"pid":"b9305da05eb1c4bb2bbbf67f7aa5b967a24e00ca","tid":922170,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"goodest logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9948f17ad4e0bed7c5f8821f5a37bd4d88c3942","tid":922170,"uid":193643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:08:11.000Z","msg":"符合國情"},{"pid":"c2929d83eb02bd1e6ac2e1b17f1865ff4c3dfa5c","tid":922170,"uid":170867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"個袋我憑我本事自己執到 有咩問題"},{"pid":"118f6ac4749be0f527c3736a0d38209a1db28c2e","tid":922170,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:09:15.000Z","msg":"滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21002934e9fc7fd4dddec9ec77235a4bf17fab17","tid":922170,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:09:48.000Z","msg":"趙女主動歸還給物主張女士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a876c988694a9e5583cfbc1e34bf94fcf349521","tid":922170,"uid":87600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"地上執到寶<br />\n問天問地攞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e7e57f1b7d7395f370234deec3fdb8e69ec052","tid":922170,"uid":61720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:10:01.000Z","msg":"啲錢喺書包入面 佢去拎<br />\n咁都唔叫偷咩..."},{"pid":"a454f61f8fdc641d533e8879ceb17543c16c330d","tid":922170,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:10:14.000Z","msg":"還強辯稱「我就是沒想還給她，我又沒偷又沒搶。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHo ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3887ce80a7996dc4bc50c012a3c7b4875f7f05","tid":922170,"uid":51387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背包裏是沒有物品掉失，但是背包內的1800元現金卻不翼而飛。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒有物品掉失, 但1800元不翼而飛. 現金唔係物品? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d01400a4534d90172004f08ac162e09615a1a1f","tid":922170,"uid":89037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"孔乙己個故事真係咩年代都啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竊書不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;竊書！&hellip;&hellip;讀書人的事，能算偷麼？"}]}